🔷 7. TRANSITION ANALYSIS (GPS → CPS)

👉 This is CRITICAL for your use case

df_sorted = df[['long_person_id','referral_id','referral_received_date','referral_type']] \
            .drop_duplicates() \
            .sort_values(['long_person_id','referral_received_date'])

df_sorted['next_type'] = df_sorted.groupby('long_person_id')['referral_type'].shift(-1)

transition = pd.crosstab(df_sorted['referral_type'], df_sorted['next_type'])
print(transition)

📊 Heatmap:

sns.heatmap(transition, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Blues')
plt.title("Referral Transition Matrix")
plt.show()


